  <h2>Today's work — choose one path</h2>
  <p class="sub">All four paths converge on the same artifact: a full OPVL with a specific Limitation. The path you pick is about how you spend the work time.</p>
  <div class="choice-intro">
    <strong>Learning Intention:</strong> I can produce a complete OPVL on the U0 Anchor Article — including a Limitation that is specific to this source, not generic to all sources.
  </div>
  <div class="choice-board">
    <div class="choice">
      <div class="choice-letter">A</div>
      <div class="choice-title">OPVL the anchor article in full (default)</div>
      <div class="choice-detail">Work the <strong>[U0 Anchor Article — TBD pending librarian]</strong> through full OPVL — 4–8 sentences across the four letters. The Limitation must be specific to this article's particular Origin / Purpose context, not generic. Carry this OPVL forward to Block 3 — you'll compare it to an AI summary OPVL tomorrow.</div>
      <span class="udl-tag">Solo · Default</span>
    </div>
    <div class="choice placeholder">
